description:
This is one of my first, rather amateurish, but really cool mashup efforts featuring Daniel Lanois&amp;#039; &quot;Duo Glide&quot; from his Here is What Is album, along with Robbie Robertson&amp;#039;s &quot;Good Day to Die&quot;, for his soundtrack for &quot;The Native Americans&quot;  

Both songs deal with the struggle of Native American cultures post Columbus.

I bought and own these files; if you like this mashup, do these guys a favor and SPEND SOME MONEY ON THEIR WEBSITES.  Lanois is at www.redfloorrecords.com.  Google Robbie Robertson, and you can find his discs, too.
